comment_text:
I am a Hongkonger and this is my personal opinion (repost) on the messages that are embedded in Sing Me To Sleep:
1: Hong Kong is a very fast going city and it is reflected in the song: in 0:04-0:05, the child said the Cantonese phrase 'Âø´Âï≤Âï¶'. Âø´Âï≤Âï¶ means telling others to do things faster. And in 0:06, the lyrics go 'wait a second let me catch my breath', which is referring to the Cantonese phrase Âø´Âï≤Âï¶.
2: Life in Hong Kong is hard: in 0:22, "Livin' life as if we had a choice" scene is filmed at The Peak, while the red point is actually located in the poorer districts in Mong Kok, Hong Kong
3: Hong Kong is cyberpunk like city: 0:47-0:51, 1:06-1:08, 1:12-1:14, 1:17-1:23 and many more sections give us the clue.
4: The disparity of rich and poor is wide in Hong Kong: Sing Me To Sleep is filmed at The Peak and Central, which are much richer places than Mong Kok, Yau Ma Tei and Tai Koo. You can see the part that is Central and The Peak are full of blue toned skyscrapers and the Mong Kok/YMT and Tai Koo part are full of old buildings, with many neon signs hanging around.

comment_text: Once there lived a girl named *LILY* in a castle with her rich and royal family. She was not allowed to go out to play and no one wanted to be her friend. She started talking with animals and always used to look at stars and count them. Her step mother did not love her. She didn't get the love of a mother from an early age. She always felt *LONELY* she was *FADED* . She always thought that she does not even have a *DIAMOND HEART* but still everyone hates her. She  *LOST CONTROL* and ran away from there. The whole kingdom started finding her but they can't find. She started living in a small town. One day she met a boy named Trev on a rainy day wearing black cloak Lily was wet in the rain the boy asked her to come under her umbrella. They started talking about each other on their way home. She told the boy that no one likes her and she is lonely. The boy asked her to come with him in his magic world. He gave her headphones. She wore it and they both held each other's hand. They were in the *DIFFERENT WORLD* where everything was opposite from Earth. It was a fantasy world. The boy was a sorcerer he made a beautiful world with his superior magic where no one can come. Their stories were same, they fell in love. They did many adventures. The girl wanted to go back on Earth for some time to meet her father. The boy let her go she promised him that she will come back here soon. She got to know that her father loves her very much. She stayed with him till his death. After her father's funeral she again started feeling lonely. She wore the headphones and came back to the boy's world. But nothing was same the colourful world was destroyed. Everything went dark and black. A boy was standing there in black hoodie and mask his name was Alan. He told the girl that the boy was a bad sorcerer, he lost his parents and after his sacrifices he became superior. But he did crimes so he was punished by a good witch. He can't control his body. The witch said that he will be only freed when someone like you starts loving you. His powers will be taken away from him and he will rebron on Earth to proof that he's good. He had ignited when she has gone and he took rebirth after few months in a good family. Now he has to proof himself. Lily said, "Again I lost my loved one. Why always me? So many sacrifices...." Alan gave her a mask and asked her to come with him in the Walker World. She met many good people. She enjoyed the adventures. But after 20 years she is still waiting for that boy when she is 36. Maybe they will meet again and that love story will continue. Ofcourse they will meet.\n\nSorry for my bad english. And I didn't think much about the story when I was writing it. So it's just something stupid. I hope that Alan will read this. Btw I wanted to watch a movie inspired by Alan Walker. But it's only a dream and it will never come true.
Name: Sing_Me_To_Sleep

comment_text: Once there lived a girl named *LILY* in a castle with her rich and royal family. She was not allowed to go out to play and no one wanted to be her friend. She started talking with animals and always used to look at stars and count them. Her step mother did not love her. She didn't get the love of a mother from an early age. She always felt *LONELY* she was *FADED* . She always thought that she does not even have a *DIAMOND HEART* but still everyone hates her. She  *LOST CONTROL* and ran away from there. The whole kingdom started finding her but they can't find. She started living in a small town. One day she met a boy named Trev on a rainy day wearing black cloak Lily was wet in the rain the boy asked her to come under her umberella. They started talking about each other on their way home. She told the boy that no one likes her and she is lonely. The boy asked her to come with him in his magic world. He gave her headphones. She wore it and they both held each other's hand. They were in the *DIFFERENT WORLD* where everything was opposite from Earth. It was a fantasy world. The boy was a sorcerer he made a beautiful world with his superior magic where no one can come. Their stories were same, they fell in love. They did many adventures. The girl wanted to go back on Earth for some time to meet her father. The boy let her go she promised him that she will come back here soon. She got to know that her father loves her very much. She stayed with him till his death. After her father's funeral she again started feeling lonely. She wore the headphones and came back to the boy's world. But nothing was same the colourful world was destroyed. Everything went dark and black. A boy was standing there in black hoodie and mask his name was Alan. He told the girl that the boy was a bad sorcerer, he lost his parents and after his sacrifices he became superior. But he did crimes so he was punished by a good witch. He can't control his body. The witch said that he will be only freed when someone like you starts loving you. His powers will be taken away from him and he will rebron on Earth to proof that he's good. He had ignited when she has gone and he took rebirth after few months in a good family. Now he has to proof himself. Lily said, "Again I lost my loved one. Why always me? So many sacrifices...." Alan gave her a mask and asked her to come with him in the Walker World. She met many good people. She enjoyed the adventures. But after 20 years she is still waiting for that boy when she is 36. Maybe they will meet again and that love story will continue. Ofcourse they will meet.\n\nSorry for my bad english. And I didn't think much about the story when I was writing it.
